	  		    		    <dt class="cell-1_2">Issued by:</dt>
		    <dd class="cell-2_2"><a href="/regulatory-information/search-fda-guidance-documents/guidance-industry-food-labeling-guide"></a>
  <div class="field field--name-field-issuing-office-taxonomy field--type-entity-reference field--label-above">
